text: Kaolack is a region in the west of Senegal. The regional capital is Kaolack. It borders Gambia. As of the 2013 census, 918,355 people lived there. It has an area of . == Départements == There are three départements: * Guinguinéo Département * Kaolack Département * Nioro du Rip Département Category:Regions of Senegal
